keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
unmap t
unmap T
unmap <a-p>
unmap <a-m>
unmap w
unmap W
unmap m
# unmap K
unmap p
unmap P
map <C-j> Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
nextPatterns: 次へ,進む,もっと見る,もっとみる,次のページ,next,more,newer,>,›,→,»,≫,>>
searchEngines:
t: https://twitter.com/search?q=%s Twitter
gh: https://github.com/search?q=%s&type=Code&utf8=✓
site: javascript:location='http://www.google.com/search?q=site:'+escape(location.hostname)+'+%s'
rn: https://renso-ruigo.com/word/%s
yy: https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s
ya: https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=asmr+%s&sp=CAM%253D
